        <section class="container has-text-centered">
            <div class="columns is-8 is-variable ">
                <div class="column is-two-third">
                    <div class="box content">
                        <article class="post has-text-left">
                            <h4>Do you have covid testing services?</h4>
                            <div class="media">
                                <div class="media-left">
                                </div>
                                <div class="media-content">
                                    <div class="content has-text-left">
                                        <p>
                                            Yes - we have covid testing services. <br><br>
                                        </p>

                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="media-right">
                                    <span class="has-text-grey-light"><i class="fa fa-comments"></i> 1</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        <article class="post has-text-left">
                            <h4>Can I call for a same day appointment for an evaluation and diagnosis?</h4>
                            <div class="media">
                                <div class="media-left">
                        
                                </div>
                                <div class="media-content">
                                    <div class="content has-text-left">
                                        <p>
                                            Yes – Please call as soon as possible if you are experiencing an urgent medical matter 
                                            that needs to be evaluated by our practice. We will do our best to fit you into the schedule 
